      "id": "PopularPost262161",
      "post_content": "This. Card. Is. Neat.  \n  \nUnless target spell wins them the game...  \n  \nTo me, this is everything I want in a counter spell, no pay ![3](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=3&type=symbol)![Colorless](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=C&type=symbol) to counter my counter...pitch your hand. If you have no hand? Goes to get me something fun like the aforementioned [Liliana of the Veil](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Liliana of the Veil), or say...[Yawgmoth's Will](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Yawgmoth's Will) or [Necropotence](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Necropotence) if you like to do broken things.",
      "posted_by": "MindAblaze",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost262161\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">This. Card. Is. Neat.<br/><br/>Unless target spell wins them the game...<br/><br/>To me, this is everything I want in a counter spell, no pay <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"3\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=3&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Colorless\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=C&amp;type=symbol\"/> to counter my counter...pitch your hand.  If you have no hand? Goes to get me something fun like the aforementioned <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Liliana of the Veil\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Liliana of the Veil\">Liliana of the Veil</a>, or say...<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Yawgmoth's Will\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Yawgmoth's Will\">Yawgmoth's Will</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Necropotence\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Necropotence\">Necropotence</a> if you like to do broken things.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '262161'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy52565\">MindAblaze</span>\r\n                                (8/12/2012 9:48:30 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div clas