    {
      "id": "PopularPost281802",
      "post_content": "A lot of people overvalue having no maximum hand size. In a reanimation deck, spellbook effects suck. I was severely hindered by my [Zedruu](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Zedruu) opponent exchanging his [Reliquary Tower](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Reliquary Tower) for one of my awesome nonbasics.  \n  \nThat aside, this is a solid all-round common with a very relevant search radius ([sword](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=sword)s, [Jace Beleren](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Jace Beleren), [Mind Funeral](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Funeral), [Temple Bell](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Temple Bell), [Memory Erosion](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Memory Erosion), [Murder](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Murder), [Dissipate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dissipate), [Capsize](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Capsize), [Corpse Dance](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Corpse Dance), [Buried Alive](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Buried Alive), [Phyrexian Arena](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Phyrexian Arena), [Trinket Mage](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Trinket Mage). . .).",
      "posted_by": "DacenOctavio",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost281802\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">A lot of people overvalue having no maximum hand size. In a reanimation deck, spellbook effects suck. I was severely hindered by my <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Zedruu\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Zedruu\">Zedruu</a> opponent exchanging his <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Reliquary Tower\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Reliquary Tower\">Reliquary Tower</a> for one of my awesome nonbasics.<br/><br/>That aside, this is a solid all-round common with a very relevant search radius (<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"sword\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=sword\">sword</a>s, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Jace Beleren\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Jace Beleren\">Jace Beleren</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mind Funeral\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Funeral\">Mind Funeral</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Temple Bell\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Temple Bell\">Temple Bell</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Memory Erosion\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Memory Erosion\">Memory Erosion</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Murder\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Murder\">Murder</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Dissipate\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dissipate\">Dissipate</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Capsize\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Capsize\">Capsize</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Corpse Dance\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Corpse Dance\">Corpse Dance</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Buried Alive\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Buried Alive\">Buried Alive</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Phyrexian Arena\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Phyrexian Arena\">Phyrexian Arena</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Trinket Mage\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Trinket Mage\">Trinket Mage</a>. . .).</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '281802'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2792\">DacenOctavio</span>\r\n                                (11/17/2012 2:20:53 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>